<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Bechen und des <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> Glancz,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und als ewr gnade schreibt, umb
                        den tag cze leisten czü Cölen <app><note><q type="date">auf den <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> sant
                            <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> tag vincula</q>01.08.1412</note></app>,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> geweiset, daz er
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag süchen und darauf gen Cöllen
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wil; und getrawen
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol, ir wollet ew den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
<expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein <expan>lasse<ex>n,</ex></expan> als
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor auch
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Wan wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> lieb und dinst
                                <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
                        Margarethe.</ab>
